node.text:
Yesterday @rcrouser said he's the only two-time Olympic champion and world record-holder without a Diamond Trophy.

Today he can add the elusive 💎 to his trophy cabinet. He wins the men's shot put with a meeting record 22.67m.

@magdalynmae wins the women’s shot put 💎 Trophy thanks to a first round 19.41m effort to complete the US shot put double.

📸 @matthewquine / @diamondleagueathletics 

#WDLFinal #diamondleague #athletics #trackandfield #shotput
